HEADWORD: Harvester
<hw>Har"vest*er</hw> <pr>(-⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>One who harvests; a machine for cutting and gathering grain; a
reaper.</def>⟦br⟧
